//BONUS
Try consuming the API from the command-line using the Bash curl program or the PowerShell Invoke-RestMethod cmdlet.

// VIEW
curl http://localhost:8080/events

// ADD
curl -H "Content-Type: application/json" -X POST -d '{"name": "Linux Fundamentals", "description": "An event for Linux enthusiasts!"}' http://localhost:8080/events/
